{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":802,"text":"I moved back home 15 years ago"},{"time":4577,"text":"after a 20-year stay in the United States,"},{"time":7441,"text":"and Africa called me back."},{"time":9805,"text":"And I founded my country's first"},{"time":13346,"text":"graphic design and new media college."},{"time":15657,"text":"And I called it the Zimbabwe\nInstitute of Vigital Arts."},{"time":20583,"text":"The idea, the dream, was really\nfor a sort of Bauhaus"},{"time":24820,"text":"sort of school where new\nideas were interrogated"},{"time":29426,"text":"and investigated,"},{"time":32639,"text":"the creation of a new visual language"},{"time":35399,"text":"based on the African creative heritage."},{"time":40380,"text":"We offer a two-year diploma"},{"time":43805,"text":"to talented students who have\nsuccessfully completed"},{"time":47569,"text":"their high school education."},{"time":49749,"text":"And typography's a very important\npart of the curriculum"},{"time":52686,"text":"and we encourage our students\nto look inward for influence."},{"time":57629,"text":"Here's a poster designed\nby one of the students"},{"time":59995,"text":"under the theme \"Education is a right.\""},{"time":64152,"text":"Some logos designed by my students."},{"time":68435,"text":"Africa has had a long\ntradition of writing,"},{"time":72503,"text":"but this is not such a well-known fact,"},{"time":74675,"text":"and I wrote the book \"Afrikan\nAlphabets\" to address that."},{"time":78608,"text":"The different types of writing in Africa,"},{"time":82155,"text":"first was proto-writing,"},{"time":84400,"text":"as illustrated by Nsibidi,"},{"time":86568,"text":"which is the writing\nsystem of a secret society"},{"time":89640,"text":"of the Ejagham people in southern Nigeria."},{"time":93470,"text":"So it's a special-interest writing system."},{"time":97340,"text":"The Akan of people of Ghana\nand [Cote d'Ivoire]"},{"time":100915,"text":"developed Adinkra symbols\nsome 400 years ago,"},{"time":104960,"text":"and these are proverbs,\nhistorical sayings,"},{"time":108828,"text":"objects, animals, plants,"},{"time":111538,"text":"and my favorite Adinkra system"},{"time":113546,"text":"is the first one at the top on the left."},{"time":115922,"text":"It's called Sankofa."},{"time":116924,"text":"It means, \"Return and get\nit.\" Learn from the past."},{"time":122918,"text":"This pictograph by the Jokwe\npeople of Angola"},{"time":125719,"text":"tells the story\nof the creation of the world."},{"time":129538,"text":"At the top is God,\nat the bottom is man, mankind,"},{"time":134942,"text":"and on the left is the sun,\non the right is the moon."},{"time":139850,"text":"All the paths lead to and from God."},{"time":143705,"text":"These secret societies\nof the Yoruba, Kongo"},{"time":148099,"text":"and Palo religions"},{"time":150294,"text":"in Nigeria, Congo and Angola respectively,"},{"time":154031,"text":"developed this intricate writing system"},{"time":157955,"text":"which is alive and well\ntoday in the New World"},{"time":161724,"text":"in Cuba, Brazil and Trinidad and Haiti."},{"time":167912,"text":"In the rainforests of the Democratic\nRepublic of Congo,"},{"time":171208,"text":"in the Ituri society,"},{"time":174099,"text":"the men pound out a cloth\nout of a special tree,"},{"time":177870,"text":"and the women, who are also\nthe praise singers,"},{"time":180963,"text":"paint interweaving patterns"},{"time":183644,"text":"that are the same in structure"},{"time":186374,"text":"as the polyphonic structures\nthat they use in their singing --"},{"time":191029,"text":"a sort of a musical score, if you may."},{"time":195017,"text":"In South Africa, Ndebele women"},{"time":197766,"text":"use these symbols and other\ngeometric patterns"},{"time":201124,"text":"to paint their homes in bright colors,"},{"time":204938,"text":"and the Zulu women use the symbols"},{"time":207860,"text":"in the beads that they weave"},{"time":209358,"text":"into bracelets and necklaces."},{"time":212501,"text":"Ethiopia has had the longest\ntradition of writing,"},{"time":216580,"text":"with the Ethiopic script\nthat was developed"},{"time":218899,"text":"in the fourth century A.D."},{"time":220861,"text":"and is used to write Amharic,"},{"time":223375,"text":"which is spoken by over 24 million people."},{"time":226660,"text":"King Ibrahim Njoya of the Bamum\nKingdom of Cameroon"},{"time":231117,"text":"developed Shü-mom at the age of 25."},{"time":234682,"text":"Shü-mom is a writing system."},{"time":236769,"text":"It's a syllabary. It's not\nexactly an alphabet."},{"time":239762,"text":"And here we see\nthree stages of development"},{"time":243077,"text":"that it went through in 30 years."},{"time":247716,"text":"The Vai people of Liberia had\na long tradition of literacy"},{"time":253276,"text":"before their first contact\nwith Europeans in the 1800s."},{"time":257211,"text":"It's a syllabary and reads\nfrom left to right."},{"time":261793,"text":"Next door, in Sierra Leone, the Mende"},{"time":265364,"text":"also developed a syllabary,"},{"time":267387,"text":"but theirs reads from right to left."},{"time":271019,"text":"Africa has had a long tradition of design,"},{"time":274409,"text":"a well-defined design sensibility,"},{"time":278032,"text":"but the problem in Africa has been that,"},{"time":280334,"text":"especially today, designers in Africa"},{"time":283032,"text":"struggle with all forms of design"},{"time":285566,"text":"because they are more apt to look outward"},{"time":290072,"text":"for influence and inspiration."},{"time":292700,"text":"The creative spirit in Africa,\nthe creative tradition,"},{"time":296897,"text":"is as potent as it has always been,"},{"time":299773,"text":"if only designers could look within."},{"time":303820,"text":"This Ethiopic cross illustrates"},{"time":306711,"text":"what Dr. Ron Eglash has established:"},{"time":309491,"text":"that Africa has a lot\nto contribute to computing"},{"time":313380,"text":"and mathematics through their intuitive\ngrasp of fractals."},{"time":318756,"text":"Africans of antiquity\ncreated civilization,"},{"time":322823,"text":"and their monuments,\nwhich still stand today,"},{"time":326136,"text":"are a true testimony of their greatness."},{"time":329720,"text":"Most probably,\none of humanity's greatest achievements"},{"time":333638,"text":"is the invention of the alphabet,"},{"time":336604,"text":"and that has been attributed\nto Mesopotamia"},{"time":339722,"text":"with their invention\nof cuneiform in 1600 BC,"},{"time":345287,"text":"followed by hieroglyphics in Egypt,"},{"time":349025,"text":"and that story has been cast\nin stone as historical fact."},{"time":354494,"text":"That is, until 1998,"},{"time":357208,"text":"when one Yale professor\nJohn Coleman Darnell"},{"time":362327,"text":"discovered these inscriptions\nin the Thebes desert"},{"time":365717,"text":"on the limestone cliffs in western Egypt,"},{"time":369077,"text":"and these have been dated\nat between 1800 and 1900 B.C.,"},{"time":375313,"text":"centuries before Mesopotamia."},{"time":378322,"text":"Called Wadi el-Hol"},{"time":381250,"text":"because of the place\nthat they were discovered,"},{"time":384456,"text":"these inscriptions --\nresearch is still going on,"},{"time":387861,"text":"a few of them have been deciphered,"},{"time":390659,"text":"but there is consensus among scholars"},{"time":393166,"text":"that this is really\nhumanity's first alphabet."},{"time":398383,"text":"Over here, you see a paleographic chart"},{"time":401427,"text":"that shows what has\nbeen deciphered so far,"},{"time":404544,"text":"starting with the letter\nA, \"ālep,\" at the top,"},{"time":407953,"text":"and \"bêt,\" in the middle, and so forth."},{"time":411638,"text":"It is time that students\nof design in Africa"},{"time":415251,"text":"read the works of titans\nlike Cheikh Anta Diop,"},{"time":419468,"text":"Senegal's Cheikh Anta Diop,"},{"time":421584,"text":"whose seminal work on Egypt is vindicated"},{"time":424667,"text":"by this discovery."},{"time":427800,"text":"The last word goes\nto the great Jamaican leader"},{"time":430887,"text":"Marcus Mosiah Garvey"},{"time":432876,"text":"and the Akan people of Ghana"},{"time":436076,"text":"with their Adinkra symbol Sankofa,"},{"time":438449,"text":"which encourages us to go to the past"},{"time":440691,"text":"so as to inform our present"},{"time":442863,"text":"and build on a future\nfor us and our children."},{"time":447465,"text":"It is also time that designers in Africa"},{"time":451706,"text":"stop looking outside."},{"time":454332,"text":"They've been looking\noutward for a long time,"},{"time":456722,"text":"yet what they were looking for"},{"time":459034,"text":"has been right there\nwithin grasp, right within them."},{"time":463987,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":465791,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}